      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, and the transmission provides clean, dependable shifts. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, the paint still holds a nice shine and the body is straight. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as they should. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
