    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? This beauty is in wonderful shape and runs like a total dream! It\u2019s been my trusty companion for daily commutes and weekend getaways, and it has never let me down. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s clean, comfy, and ready for many more miles of memories. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
