    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, and the subframe has been proactively inspected for structural integrity. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and valve adjustment. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp, offering an authentic analog performance profile.",
      "price": 34500.0,
